#

Whole Grain Waffles

30 min
$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianHigh Fiber

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchHealthy

Description

Fluffy and wholesome, these whole grain waffles are perfect for a delightful breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • whole wheat flour: 1 cup
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • baking soda: 1/2 tsp
  • salt: 1/4 tsp
  • milk: 1 cup
  • eggs: 2
  • honey or maple syrup: 2 tbsp
  • vegetable oil or melted butter: 2 tbsp
